sub_title: MA student at Utrecht University | Global Criminology
summary:
I’m currently completing an MA in Global Criminology in the Netherlands, after recently obtaining a Graduate Certificate in Victimology and a BA in Criminology and Criminal Justice in Canada. 

I am currently interested in working in the compliance and risk sector or as an analyst in a field relevant to criminology. 

I am bilingual (English and French) and would be willing to relocate.
